{"id":"2db80a57-1c8a-429b-af0e-51766ef5af8a","name":"Corrin (Female)","description":"<p>A Hoshidan princess raised in Nohr. Fights on her chose path with the divine blade Yato. Appears in Fire Emblem Fates.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/b3u_dqr8JBM7lYX6aQXRu.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Corrin is a Hero who endured a difficult fate, being born a princess of Hoshido yet brought up believing she was a princess of Nohr.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UU8x1Rs88VI7S0nV6795R.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">She was only a young child when she was stolen away to Nohr, and it wasn't until the war between Hoshido and Nohr began that she learned of her true origins.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nODzON-BZ8tmroz7erX4r.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">That was when she encountered Hoshido's army on the battlefield. Caught between two kingdoms, she agonized over where she truly belonged...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/h1nvP4ydtPmD0ec6tItqo.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">In the end, she made her choice. Whatever awaits at the end of the path she chose to tread, she walks ever on, believing in the future!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ML1kfCBoPRTAl8CemUh1w.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Full Art By: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://feheroes.fandom.com/wiki/Bthx\" target=\"_blank\">bthx</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7XuW7qgt7OGoZ9P_VAKtr.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"TYHOHInByjZd0S9cYcBy3.webp","creator":"Denki_The_Thunder_King27","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👑 Royalty","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":85,"messages":637,"created_at":"2025-12-15T01:59:19.954486+00:00"}